{"_path":"/maps/_ai/vibe/vibe","_dir":"vibe","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Vibe Coding","description":"Vibe 是一种基于 AI 的代码生成和协作方式，旨在通过自然语言提示帮助开发者快速生成代码片段、自动化任务和提升编程效率。","original_path":"_ai/vibe.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"domain"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Domain"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"基础配置"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基础配置"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/vibe/agents-md"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"agents.md"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"编写-agentsmd-的关键要点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"编写 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"agents.md"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的关键要点？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CLAUDE.md 是每次会话默认载入的文件，用来在编码代理启动时把代码库信息传给 Claude。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM 本质上无状态，代理一开始对代码库一无所知。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CLAUDE.md 应只包含“WHAT/WHY/HOW”：技术栈、项目结构、目的以及如何运行测试等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免把所有命令和风格规范塞进去，LLM 能跟随的指令数有限（≈150‑200）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"保持文件短小，最好 <300 行；更短越好。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用渐进式披露：把任务专属说明拆成单独 Markdown，CLAUDE.md 只列出指向并让 Claude 决定是否读取。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"别把代码风格规则放进 CLAUDE.md；让 linters/formatters 处理，LLM 用来写代码即可。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Claude 会在系统提醒中自动忽略不相关内容，越通用的指令越有可能被采纳。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"切勿自动生成 CLAUDE.md；每一行都要经过精心策划，以免产生错误的实现。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.humanlayer.dev/blog/writing-a-good-claude-md","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Writing a good CLAUDE.md"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"规模化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"规模化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/vibe/team-of-agents"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Team of Agents"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"持续集成"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续集成"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/vibe/anchoring"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Anchoring coding agents to a ref application"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/vibe/complacency"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Complacency in AI-assisted coding"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"设计思维"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"设计思维"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/vibe/playful-ai"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"玩具化设计思维"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 将复杂 AI 能力转化为情感化、游戏化体验"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"暗面与风险"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"暗面与风险"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"vibescammingai-降低了诈骗的技术门槛"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"VibeScamming：AI 降低了诈骗的技术门槛"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vibe coding 不仅被用于正当开发，也正被滥用为\"VibeScamming\"——\n利用 AI 工具几乎零技术门槛地创建专业级垃圾邮件和诈骗方案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"诈骗者只需几个提示词，就能生成窃取信用卡信息、钓鱼 Office365 凭证等的完整方案。\nAnthropic 的报告指出，即使是\"无代码\"的勒索软件，现在也能由完全不会编程的人通过 LLM 构建，并以高达 1200 美元的价格出售。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这种趋势带来了双重问题：垃圾邮件的视觉质量提升使传统识别方法失效；\n而 vibe-coded 应用的特定视觉风格（过多的 chrome、颜色和表情符号）\n反而可能让正当的 AI 辅助开发作品看起来不可信。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tedium.co/2026/02/25/vibe-coded-email-spam/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Why Email Spam Looks Better Than Usual These Days"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"links"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Links"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"余额查询"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"余额查询"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/settings/billing/budgets","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Copilot"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.trae.ai/account-setting?user_id=7473336841417851912&username=Lionad-Morotar#usage","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Trae"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"domain","depth":2,"text":"Domain","children":[{"id":"基础配置","depth":3,"text":"基础配置"},{"id":"规模化","depth":3,"text":"规模化"},{"id":"持续集成","depth":3,"text":"持续集成"},{"id":"设计思维","depth":3,"text":"设计思维"},{"id":"暗面与风险","depth":3,"text":"暗面与风险"}]},{"id":"links","depth":2,"text":"Links"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:vibe:vibe.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/vibe/vibe.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/vibe/vibe","_extension":"md"}